Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来总算得到禁术了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 萤 很壮观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是禁术的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我共同完成的艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:00:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把诗形大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可让人头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容器可不需要感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是土蜘蛛的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那些烦人的家伙全都烧光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁之术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们最后不得不打倒村民了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不在乎他们会如何哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸 行 无 常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弁天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人的联合忍术虽然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就剩下两人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能赢我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个禁术来控制小国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借此动摇五大国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让你得手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形 现在可不是你休息的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须夺回萤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知死活的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再接一次禁术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术.爆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形 你趁机去救萤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术.炎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这就完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就不能结印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要加倍还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想让禁术…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道 或许是自然能量吸收得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快将它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这个状态怎么可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术不管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比刚才还厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样继续吸收自然查克拉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终会把村子一起炸飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土蜘蛛一族的复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,役之行者的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于大人们一厢情愿的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤看来也承受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不懂萤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直独自保护禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了一族的复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑着献出了自己的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自承受了这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 跟诗形邂逅之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被骗了 不过遇到你这个师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤终于有了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于拥有了羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一切都让你摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么同伴 羁绊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这种天真的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟萤的遭遇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是弟子还是儿子都可以牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是忍者的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我体验过太多 已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了曾是我的师父的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺取禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我俩做的事一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父无论何时都会为弟子着想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论离得多远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心愿都能让人感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时 都在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤也一定感觉到了爷爷 遁兵卫 还有诗形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法 肯定已经传递给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定就在她的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她仍然在寻求和同伴 师父的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个一无所知的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许说这种自以为是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就吼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术.割
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在容器失控前暂且撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把白浪带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是萤的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就待在她的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤也一定感觉到了爷爷 遁兵卫 还有诗形
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的想法 肯定已经传递给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法 在她的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒冲昏了我的头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父的想法 还有留存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父的想法 已经传递给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形 活下去 和这份力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓不再使用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为了萤借给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害了鸣人和诗形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人和我都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背叛了诗形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和禁术一起消失就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会看你这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟子就该听师父的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父…的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的力量 已经抑制不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 我会被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术会爆发了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信师父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把这个村子彻底摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这一切都毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术.炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你 我绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字缚之术.斩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点带他去萤那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人操心的弟子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好萤没事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土蜘蛛一族和木叶村约定的任务就全部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁术虽然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样萤小姐也不会再被人盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民也会同意接受萤的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是打算和诗形一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有许多需要学习的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要接受师父的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为能为土蜘蛛一族复兴而出力的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开我的玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 你终于肯做她的师傅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那萤就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 各位请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有师父果然是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有点想好色仙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我第一次遇见师父的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 可以在这里稍等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去见雾忍暗部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要得到和你一起修行的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没有回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑他们出什么意外了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六尾人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们干掉了剑他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要重建世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此你是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是你体内的尾兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六尾我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 你要活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倏地传来了自来也的噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这突如其来的消息 让同伴们深受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们手足无措 举步维艰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻的木叶吹起了悲伤的暴风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集火影疾风传 噩耗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 五代大人叫你呢
